-- Madagascar Central Bank to Be Sole Gold Exporter, l’Express Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-06-29T11:17:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-29/madagascar-central-bank-to-be-sole-gold-exporter-l-express-says.html
Madagascar’s central bank will be
the only entity allowed to export gold, l’Express de Madagascar
reported, citing a statement from the government.  Buyers will be selected via an international tender, the
Antananarivo-based newspaper reported on its  website  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
